  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Nimal took the post",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Member of Parliament Nimal Siripala de Silva was sworn in as the Minister of Ports, Shipping and Aviation.",
        "Following the allegations leveled against him, he was removed from his ministerial post by the then President Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "Thereafter, a committee conducted an investigation. Its report was handed over to President's Secretary Kamini Senaratne.",
        "In it, none of the allegations against Nimal Siripaladi Silva have been proved. After that, Nimal Siripaladi Silva accepted his ministerial post."
      ],
